content:
 Fixed the animation carton problem in the lower left column;
Fixed the problem of switching between the Chinese and English interfaces;
Fixed the problem of avatar display;
Fixed the problem of counting function and solved the problem of calling Umami API;
Launched WSwriter, a website article writing and pushing assistant, to meet the needs of writing in the office-like interface without the IDE interface, supporting one-click preview, submission, modification, and deletion of articles, as well as inserting code, images, and tables;
Added commenting function;
Fixed the error of double quotes when adding tags to WSwriter;
The security of the website has been maintained.
